                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>all the public or private surplus funds<lb/> at command. Our city unlike\n                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> has among our people few wealthy\n                persons,<lb/> and the few have such constant calls<lb/> at home, that they are\n                unable to lend<lb/> or give abroad. With <sic>with</sic> my<lb/> warmest regards I\n                am</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours Very Respy</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\"><persName role=\"author\">Geo Jonas</persName> President</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Congregation “Dispersed of Judah”</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
